  "prompt": "Some popular singers who have similar voice (eg:like Rihanna and Era (bonbon singer)?",
  "response": "Certainly! If you're looking for popular singers with vocal styles similar to **Rihanna** and **Era**, here are some artists you might enjoy:\n\n### **Similar to Rihanna:**\nRihanna is known for her versatile voice, blending pop, R&B, and Caribbean influences. Here are some artists with comparable styles:\n\n1. **SZA**\n   - **Style:** Contemporary R&B with soulful melodies.\n   - **Notable Songs:** \"Good Days,\" \"The Weekend\"\n\n2. **Dua Lipa**\n   - **Style:** Pop with a touch of disco and electronic influences.\n   - **Notable Songs:** \"Don't Start Now,\" \"Levitating\"\n\n3. **Kehlani**\n   - **Style:** Smooth R&B and neo-soul.\n   - **Notable Songs:** \"CRZY,\" \"Distraction\"\n\n4. **H.E.R.**\n   - **Style:** Modern R&B with emotional depth.\n   - **Notable Songs:** \"Best Part,\" \"Focus\"\n\n5. **Normani**\n   - **Style:** Pop and R&B with strong vocal performances.\n   - **Notable Songs:** \"Motivation,\" \"Wild Side\"\n\n### **Similar to Era:**\nAssuming you're referring to **Era**, the project known for its ethno-classical and new age music, here are some artists with a similar atmospheric and fusion style:\n\n1. **Enya**\n   - **Style:** New age, ethno-pop with layered vocals.\n   - **Notable Songs:** \"Only Time,\" \"May It Be\"\n\n2. **Lisa Gerrard**\n   - **Style:** Ethereal and ambient, often blending classical and world music.\n   - **Notable Works:** Soundtrack for \"Gladiator,\" collaborations with Dead Can Dance\n\n3. **Loreena McKennitt**\n   - **Style:** Celtic and world music with rich storytelling.\n   - **Notable Songs:** \"The Mummers' Dance,\" \"Falls of the Sila\"\n\n4. **Kitaro**\n   - **Style:** New age instrumental with world music influences.\n   - **Notable Albums:** \"Silk Road,\" \"Sacred Journey\"\n\n5. **Vangelis**\n   - **Style:** Synth-driven ambient and orchestral compositions.\n   - **Notable Works:** Soundtrack for \"Blade Runner,\" \"Chariots of Fire\"\n\n### **Additional Recommendations:**\nIf you're looking for artists who blend pop with unique vocal textures or atmospheric sounds, consider:\n\n- **Florence + The Machine** \u2013 Powerful vocals with indie and baroque pop influences.\n- **Banks** \u2013 Dark pop and alternative R&B with moody atmospheres.\n- **Imagine Dragons** \u2013 While more on the rock side, they incorporate diverse vocal styles and production elements.\n\n### **Conclusion:**\nBoth **Rihanna** and **Era** represent distinct musical styles\u2014Rihanna with her blend of pop and R&B, and Era with atmospheric, ethno-classical sounds. Depending on which aspect of their vocals or styles you enjoy, the artists listed above should offer a variety of similar listening experiences. Let me know if you need more specific recommendations or information on any of these artists!",
